    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>故事</u>： 安德烈因工作关系搬到了莫斯科，并在一栋板房里租了一套公寓，这符合他的预算。住进去不久，他开始注意到每天晚上都有奇怪的事情发生。有人敲门，或者门自己开了，然后半夜会有奇怪的声音把我吵醒。白天，一切似乎又恢复了正常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房东太太忘了提醒安德烈会有邻居和他同居在一套公寓里。她只是在安德烈搬进来之后才提醒他，并留下了一张纸条，说他应该保持安静，不要发出声音，也不要去不该去的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事的中心--公寓，游戏的主要情节就发生在这里。在这里，安德鲁遇到了之前住在公寓里的陌生邻居。半夜醒来，安德烈观察邻居，探索上锁的房间，研究他们留下的笔记。就这样，他发现自己被困在了这栋公寓里，而这栋公寓过去看起来就像是苏联老建筑里的廉价住房。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>游戏特色</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 典型的现世现实情节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 行走模拟器 &quot;类型的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 时间不超过一小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 揭开神秘邻居的可怕秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 揭露秘密的后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 我们时代的苏联公寓氛围。</p>",
